{"tid":899461,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Fb主管去年被炒 或與支持特朗普有關","createTime":"2018-11-12T12:40:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-12T14:41:05.000Z","uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"de6be8ce9ee83e5065db2d344cc1b3a616b8e93e","tid":899461,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T12:40:30.000Z","msg":"《華爾街日報》引述消息人士稱，去年離職的Facebook(fb)虛擬實景項目主管Palmer Luckey向友人透露，離職原因是他支持總統特朗普，以及他的政治看法。<br />\nLuckey在2016年向一個反希拉莉團體提供1萬美元捐款。事件曝光後，他被同僚炮轟，6個月後離職。事後，fb與他一直沒有公開談及離職原因。<br />\n報道指，他當時實際上是先被勒令停職，然後再被革職。據悉，在他被停職及解僱期間，fb高層曾經在電郵通訊內討論此事。據悉，fb行政總裁朱克伯格要求Luckey公開支持另一名自由派總統候選人Gary Johnson，而不是特朗普。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/international/article/1989218/fb%E4%B8%BB%E7%AE%A1%E5%8E%BB%E5%B9%B4%E8%A2%AB%E7%82%92+%E6%88%96%E8%88%87%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E6%9C%89%E9%97%9C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Finternational%2Farticle%2F1989218%2Ffb%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E5%258E%25BB%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E7%2582%2592%2B%25E6%2588%2596%25E8%2588%2587%25E6%2594%25AF%25E6%258C%2581%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%2599%25AE%25E6%259C%2589%25E9%2597%259C&d=78rhoyQhFmF23lo6MDXfm7%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=95758257\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/international/article/1989218/fb%E4%B8%BB%E7%AE%A1%E5%8E%BB%E5%B9%B4%E8%A2%AB%E7%82%92+%E6%88%96%E8%88%87%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E6%9C%89%E9%97%9C</a>"},{"pid":"2010702f4ad505cec9724cafa3de342dc7988c20","tid":899461,"uid":24615,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T13:54:24.000Z","msg":"左膠以大愛 先進思想為名 行獨裁為實"},{"pid":"e043dc68774da82f2fb054f67775c1f676672cd2","tid":899461,"uid":26770,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"2010702f4ad505cec9724cafa3de342dc7988c20","tid":899461,"uid":24615,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T13:54:24.000Z","msg":"左膠以大愛 先進思想為名 行獨裁為實"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T13:57:58.000Z","msg":"大撚把人屌左膠屌大陸人比FACEBOOK 停ACC<br />\n但5毛就點PORT都無事"},{"pid":"1da6f42defae36aba3a0bfbad5c9213de142afde","tid":899461,"uid":37524,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T14:00:08.000Z","msg":"FB本身都係垃圾公司嚟"},{"pid":"9be9e755d68f0307a096bd12793f6b225fc5049a","tid":899461,"uid":48234,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T14:41:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">Mark Fuckerberg呢條撚樣娶咗蚑那臭閪<br />\n咁大家明咩事啦屌你老母</span></span>"}]}